Read AGENTS.md first.

Project: 朕的一生, a vertical mobile H5 Reigns-like game.

Primary rules:
- Keep MVP gameplay to one card, left/right swipe, four-resource balance, frequent endings, and quick restart.
- Use data-driven cards from data/chinese-reigns/.
- Do not add complex management systems to MVP.
- Maintain the SBTI-lowpoly visual direction.
- Update docs/agentic-coding/progress-log.md when completing meaningful work.

